    "description": "<strong>Out of the Mist</strong> is a game where you master a unique control scheme. Instead of controlling the character directly, manipulate the environment to your advantage. Learn to navigate challenging platforming sections to reach the heart of this realm. Can you conquer the obstacles and unravel the mysteries hidden within the mist?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Traverse atmospheric landscapes</h2>Embark on journey where you traverse captivating environments while trying to reach the golden throne. Immerse yourself in stunning visuals and a mesmerizing soundscape as you strive to reach your goal.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886930/extras/46ad5b6f2cd608404a04657329dff877.poster.avif?t=1691927417\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886930/extras/46ad5b6f2cd608404a04657329dff877.webm?t=1691927417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886930/extras/46ad5b6f2cd608404a04657329dff877.mp4?t=1691927417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master the environment</h2>You don’t control your character, but rather the environment around him. Learn how to use this to your advantage to achieve your goals and master challenging platforming in order to get to the golden throne!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886930/extras/e5d085fc1df2cd2676c976bc554a5ac0.poster.avif?t=1691927417\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886930/extras/e5d085fc1df2cd2676c976bc554a5ac0.webm?t=1691927417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steams